心諗大個仔同諗你幅body無衝突<br />\n<br />\n即使你AA 睇左就會有印象</blockquote><br />\n唉屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁大個女都未比男友以外睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連我老豆係我有記憶以來都冇見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似係</blockquote><br />\n你細個時老豆應該望過"},{"pid":"7fd49154e14cc6bd1cbf40e4261959f2faedc4fb","tid":348200,"uid":124146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:12:40.000Z","msg":"唔止一次 即係仲會有下次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e544fcebf923bd527cefde5a799addf3c56827a0","tid":348200,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:12:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪西都睇埋?</blockquote><br />\n頂盡睇到毛<br />\n樓主唔會癲到反埋西比人睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係就唔止心理準備，仲要行動準備埋比人扑</blockquote><br />\n頂盡睇到毛 你應該都唔剃毛架啦"},{"pid":"27d21bf4f13cc975773fa5572d6a6a65c79c031e","tid":348200,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:15:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你地係廳搞野?</blockquote><br />\n唔係呀<br />\n但唔講咁多會比人起底<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁佢睇完，你地有冇講d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢有冇呆左幾秒咁打量你全身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇啦<br />\n大家都係當冇事發生<br />\n但我自己真係尷到核爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地老豆睇唔小呢d 小兒科姐"},{"pid":"0876b02c3dec5cb50a59ba3e6fbd890e6cf4bb89","tid":348200,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:16:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我試過一次同我女友扑緊嘢阿媽返咗黎話漏咗野要拎返 我聽到鐵閘聲即刻同佢跑入廁所 我扮痾屎佢躲喺沖涼個度 好彩最後無俾我媽發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n伯母最後唔知你條女黎過？"},{"pid":"c96e6408f1b7848f78f2cc3dd48