/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef651d51c172c3199aa5bde8aa29839dd36c8e9","tid":348200,"uid":72258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:59:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下次小心啲啦絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同佢講返 我已經食緊你個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22919881b7c227ef4092d4f22068f2b815568967","tid":348200,"uid":123651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T13:04:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下次小心啲啦絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同佢講返 我已經食緊你個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594bb116a5c9bdcbea248ab2665d3c16c9bf6057","tid":348200,"uid":125079,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T13:27:48.000Z","msg":"睇完依個post留言既唯一感想係，香港地土地空間不足，一個安全扑野既地方都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1585146012a08a241db77c3489c7fd0bb048dc51","tid":348200,"uid":86051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:50:59.000Z","msg":"成班唔鎖門咩心態？"},{"pid":"78027ce8c52adcfc38c224cc729630d60df46cab","tid":348200,"uid":66759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T16:07:33.000Z","msg":"三個男人。。。好想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"272e24392eb7386445ebe0a9afa808dc55916b09","tid":348200,"uid":43096,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T16:56:50.000Z","msg":"你阿爸見到大概係咁??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 